    "category": "Long Running Job Failure",
    "severity": "Sev-1 (Critical)",
    "description": "Long Running Job Failure incident on the Orders pipeline (RTL_ORD_LRJF): finance intercompany reconciliation fails on referential integrity.",
    "symptoms": "Month-end intercompany reconciliation DAG fails after 3h15m on a foreign-key violation when loading into the FINANCE.RECON_FACT table.",
    "root_cause": "A newly onboarded subsidiary's chart-of-accounts mapping was missing from the SUP.GL_MAPPING dimension, so incoming GL entries referenced entity codes with no matching dimension row.",
    "business_impact": "Month-end close blocked entity-wide until the mapping gap is resolved, risking a 1-day close delay reported to the CFO.",
    "resolution": "Add the missing subsidiary mapping rows; add a pre-load referential-integrity check task that fails fast (in minutes, not hours) instead of failing at final load."
  },
